## Backstory

Delta Spirit is a rock band from San Diego, California with a sound that's a blend of Indie Rock, Alt-Country, and&nbsp;[Americana](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Americana_\(music\)). In 2007 they produced and recorded their first album, "Ode to Sunshine", in a cabin in the San Diego mountains. They've made appearances on Conan O'Brien's and Cason Daly's talk shows and many others. In 2012 they released their third studio album, self-titled "Delta Spirit", recorded and produced by Chris Coady. [Chris Coady](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chris_Coady) is known for his work with acts like Slowdive, Beach House, Santigold, Yeah Yeah Yeahs, Massive Attack, and Grizzly Bear to name a few. The album "Delta Spirit" reached #1 on Billboard 200's Heatseekers chart. The single "California" was widely played on the radio throughout their hometown of San Diego.

Delta Spirit's music has been featured in many shows including, [Friday Night Lights](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Friday_Night_Lights_\(TV_series\)), [Sons of Anarchy](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sons_of_Anarchy), [Grey's Anatomy](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grey%27s_Anatomy), [The Walking Dead](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Walking_Dead_\(TV_series\)), and [American Dad!](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/American_Dad!). In 2014 Delta Spirit released "Into the Wide" and its become their highest charting album in the United States.

---

## Analysis

Delta Spirit has a ton of great tracks. Here are a few great songs ranging from alt-country to indie rock.

### Ode to Sunshine (2008)

#### Track 1 - Tomorrow Goes Away

{% Player
   trackId="6JSWqiggSXO5ujah8fkUOL"
   trackArtist="Delta Spirit"
   trackName="Tomorrow Goes Away"
   trackAlbumArt="delta-spirit-ode-to-sunshine-2007"
   platformLinks={spotify: "https://open.spotify.com/track/6JSWqiggSXO5ujah8fkUOL", youtube: "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZIEtP_jEiv0", appleMusic: "https://music.apple.com/us/song/tomorrow-goes-away/1489231036", deezer: "https://link.deezer.com/s/333x8oDAbe8yebIV0YByp", soundcloud: "https://soundcloud.com/deltaspirit/tomorrow-goes-away?in=deltaspirit/sets/ode-to-sunshine&si=ea9e766e9c3040a9863873b56bf44d28"} /%}

Delta Spirit has a strong country sound as one can quickly tell in "Tomorrow Goes Away". The track feels almost beatles-like in terms of composition and vocals. It's an excellent track to introduce listener's to the band's wonderful vocals and harmonies.

#### Track 6 - Streetwalker

{% Player
   trackId="4SCobBx8k3ZXNvj17o1NZc"
