#### Track 7 - People Turn Around

{% Iframe
   code="<iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/iZ2Y2vTsr70?rel=0\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>" /%}

Using the live version here because not only does it demonstrate Delta Spirit's musical talent but honestly sounds better than the studio version. It also allows you to see the passion with which the band sings. They all have really commanding voices and have good harmonies. "People Turn Around" is a call for people to be nicer to each other. The song itself is tame and soft but works in helping the voice and its message out. Its a sincere song intended to reach the listener.

> Turn around\
For the life we've been living, messing around\
The blood we've been spilling will bleed us dry\
The life we've been killing is your life like mine

