#### Track 10 - St. Francis

{% Player
   trackId="1evKhmNlyOwx2EqYyFB8YB"
   trackArtist="Delta Spirit"
   trackName="St. Francis"
   trackAlbumArt="delta-spirit-history-from-below-2010"
   platformLinks={spotify: "https://open.spotify.com/track/1evKhmNlyOwx2EqYyFB8YB", youtube: "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6hgRbPDTqlQ", appleMusic: "https://music.apple.com/us/song/st-francis/1443137906", deezer: "https://link.deezer.com/s/333xdj4aveNOdqcJaR7Qd", soundcloud: "https://soundcloud.com/deltaspirit/st-francis?in=deltaspirit/sets/history-from-below&si=4848dae43f924e24b97bd0a15b17243f"} /%}

"St. Francis" has&nbsp; a beautiful western guitar and harmonica sound. The piano and horn adornments really make the song more beautiful than it already is. The vocals are coarse and display "Delta Spirit's" great harmonies as in other tracks. The song talks about running away from one's issues thinking money and the big city will provide a solution. Even worse when we receive advice we tend to ignore it and proceed to act the way we want, thinking there's nothing wrong.

